    </datafield>
    <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
      <subfield code="a">Decoration: Texblock border-ruled in red, gold, dark blue; rubrications in red; page-opening frame-ruled in gold.</subfield>
    </datafield>
    <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
      <subfield code="a">Binding: Lacquered boards; plain black outside covers, red inside covers with painted central mandorla and two pendants on the vertical axis.</subfield>
    </datafield>
    <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
