    </datafield>
    <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
      <subfield code="a">Catalog entry in English and description of the manuscript in French in ink pasted onto last flyleaf recto; catalog entry in English, number 237, and bookplate for Le Ch. Ferrão de Castelbranco (inside front cover).</subfield>
    </datafield>
